<paragraph blockId="5.[151,1437,153,359]" pageId="5" pageNumber="156">
A checklist of species and species-groups, with corresponding old names, is presented in 
<tableCitation box="[1221,1339,297,323]" captionStart="TABLE 1" captionStartId="5.[151,244,404,431]" captionTargetBox="[186,1304,482,627]" captionTargetPageId="5" captionText="TABLE 1. Checklist of Pygopleurus species and subspecies here recognised for mainland Greece, and previous treatment for each taxon." httpUri="http://table.plazi.org/id/DF266646C155842EFF0CFE44FE3D8CC4" pageId="5" pageNumber="156" tableUuid="DF266646C155842EFF0CFE44FE3D8CC4">Table 1. A</tableCitation>
detailed taxonomic account follows, with species arranged as in the table.
</paragraph>
